---
export const prerender = true;

import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About kira w.">
  <div class="container py-5">
    <div class="row justify-content-center">
      <div class="col-lg-7">

        <h1 style="font-size:1.6rem;margin-bottom:0.25rem;">About</h1>
        <p style="color:var(--text-muted);font-size:0.875rem;margin-bottom:3rem;">The person behind the blog</p>

        <div class="prose">
          <p>
            Hi, I'm Kira. I'm a high school sophomore who does a lot of things —
            piano, violin, math, CS, textbooks — and is maybe only mediocre at a lot
            of them, but hey, it's fun.
          </p>
          <p>
            Right now I'm working through Apostol Calculus Vol. 1, jumping between
            math projects and CS side projects, and trying to build a life I really
            love. I want to be curious.
          </p>
          <p>
            This blog is a record of things I've worked through and thought about.
            The math and CS posts are write-ups of things I've learned or built.
            The essays are thinking out loud.
          </p>

          <h2>Contact</h2>
          <p>
            Email: <a href="mailto:kikisadventures37@gmail.com">kikisadventures37@gmail.com</a>
          </p>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
